{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-attribute/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/selector-combinator-whitelist/","description":"selector-id-pattern 指定 ID 选择器的模式。 选项 regex|string 字符串将被翻译成一个正则表达式，就像 new RegExp(yourString) ———— 所以一定要正确转义。 此规则将检查 # 之后的选择器值。无需在模式中包含 #。…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"selector-id-pattern\"><a href=\"#selector-id-pattern\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>selector-id-pattern</h1>\n<p>指定 ID 选择器的模式。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span>, <span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#bar</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.baz</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span>, <span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#hoo</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[disabled]</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**   ↑           ↑\n * 这些 ID 选择器 */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>regex|string</code></p>\n<p>字符串将被翻译成一个正则表达式，就像 <code>new RegExp(yourString)</code> ———— 所以一定要正确转义。</p>\n<p>此规则将检查 <em><code>#</code> 之后</em>的选择器值。无需在模式中包含 <code>#</code>。</p>\n<p>给定字符串：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"foo-[a-z]+\"</span></code></pre>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#foop</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#foo-BAR</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> > <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.zing</span> + <span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#foo-BAR</span> {}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#foo-bar</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">div</span> > <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.zing</span> + <span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#foo-bar</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foop</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[foo='bar']</span> {}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/selector-id-pattern.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/selector-id-pattern/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-id-pattern/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-id-pattern/index.html.cba48a08279f875febf082bd3e4ce95d.json"}